== Events == * {{ill|Chūhira|ja|中平|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 6th year（{{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|189|ja|189|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|September 30|ja|9月30日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – {{ill|Later Han|ja|後漢|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} の都・{{ill|Luoyang|ja|洛陽|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} を占領した {{ill|Dong Zhuo|ja|董卓|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} が {{ill|Shaodi Bian|ja|少帝弁|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} を廃し {{ill|Xian Di (Han)|ja|献帝 (漢)|lt=Xian Di|lt_ja=献帝|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} を擁立
== Births == * {{ill|Engi|ja|延喜|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 12nd year（{{ill|912|ja|912|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|October 15|ja|10月15日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – {{ill|Ryōgen|ja|良源|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 、{{ill|Tendai sect|ja|天台宗|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 中興の祖（+ {{ill|985|ja|985|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） * {{ill|Ōhō|ja|応保|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 1st year（{{ill|1161|ja|1161|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|September 23|ja|9月23日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – {{ill|Taka-kura Tennō|ja|Emperor Takakura|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 、80代 {{ill|Emperor|ja|天皇|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} （+ {{ill|1181|ja|1181|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） * {{ill|Tenshō|ja|天正|1=Tenshō (Momoyama period)|lt=Tenshō Era|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 11th year（{{ill|1583|ja|1583|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|October 18|ja|10月18日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – {{ill|Takeda Shinyoshi|ja|武田信吉|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 、{{ill|Tokugawa Ieyasu|ja|徳川家康|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} の五男（+ {{ill|1603|ja|1603|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） * {{ill|Enpō|ja|延宝|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 3rd year（{{ill|1675|ja|1675|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|October 21|ja|10月21日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – {{ill|Tōzan Tennō|ja|東山天皇|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 、113代天皇（+ {{ill|1709|ja|1709|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） * {{ill|Bunka (era)|ja|文化 (元号)|lt=Bunka|lt_ja=文化|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 5th year（{{ill|1808|ja|1808|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|October 22|ja|10月22日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – {{ill|Sakai Tadayoshi (Isesaki Domain)|ja|酒井忠良 (伊勢崎藩主)|lt=Sakai Tadayoshi|lt_ja=酒井忠良|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 、{{ill|Isesaki Domain|ja|伊勢崎藩|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 主（+ {{ill|1834|ja|1834|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ）
== Deaths == * {{ill|Kōan|ja|弘安|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 9th year（{{ill|1286|ja|1286|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|September 22|ja|9月22日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – {{ill|Mukaku Sogen|ja|無学祖元|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 、{{ill|Rinzai sect|ja|臨済宗|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} の {{ill|monk|ja|Monk侶|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} （* {{ill|1226|ja|1226|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） * {{ill|Bunpō|ja|文保|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 1st year（{{ill|1317|ja|1317|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|October 8|ja|10月8日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – {{ill|Fushimi Tennō|ja|伏見天皇|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 、92代 {{ill|Emperor|ja|天皇|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} （* {{ill|1265|ja|1265|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） * {{ill|Kan'ei|ja|寛永|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 9th year（{{ill|1632|ja|1632|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|October 16|ja|10月16日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – {{ill|Asano Nagamasa|ja|浅野長晟|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 、{{ill|Ashimori Domain|ja|足守藩|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 主、{{ill|Kishū Domain|ja|紀州藩|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 主、{{ill|Hiroshima Domain|ja|広島藩|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 主（* {{ill|1586|ja|1586|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} )
