{{Lunisolar September}} 
'''September 3''' is the 3rd day of month {{ill|September (Lunisolar)|ja|9月 (旧暦)|lt=September|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  the 9th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} . It's {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  day is {{ill|Taian|ja|大安|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} .

== Events ==
* {{ill|Chūhira|ja|中平|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 6th year（{{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|189|ja|189|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|September 30|ja|9月30日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – {{ill|Later Han|ja|後漢|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  の都・{{ill|Luoyang|ja|洛陽|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  を占領した {{ill|Dong Zhuo|ja|董卓|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  が {{ill|Shaodi Bian|ja|少帝弁|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  を廃し {{ill|Xian Di (Han)|ja|献帝 (漢)|lt=Xian Di|lt_ja=献帝|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  を擁立

== Births ==
* {{ill|Engi|ja|延喜|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 12nd year（{{ill|912|ja|912|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|October 15|ja|10月15日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – {{ill|Ryōgen|ja|良源|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 、{{ill|Tendai sect|ja|天台宗|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  中興の祖（+ {{ill|985|ja|985|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ）
* {{ill|Ōhō|ja|応保|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 1st year（{{ill|1161|ja|1161|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|September 23|ja|9月23日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – {{ill|Taka-kura Tennō|ja|Emperor Takakura|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 、80代 {{ill|Emperor|ja|天皇|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} （+ {{ill|1181|ja|1181|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ）
* {{ill|Tenshō|ja|天正|1=Tenshō (Momoyama period)|lt=Tenshō Era|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 11th year（{{ill|1583|ja|1583|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|October 18|ja|10月18日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – {{ill|Takeda Shinyoshi|ja|武田信吉|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 、{{ill|Tokugawa Ieyasu|ja|徳川家康|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  の五男（+ {{ill|1603|ja|1603|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ）
* {{ill|Enpō|ja|延宝|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 3rd year（{{ill|1675|ja|1675|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|October 21|ja|10月21日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – {{ill|Tōzan Tennō|ja|東山天皇|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 、113代天皇（+ {{ill|1709|ja|1709|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ）
